extendedInfo.description: The Green Bay Area Chamber of Commerce app provides quick and easy access to the Chamber's ever-popular, search able membership directory, calendar of events, contact information, Chamber accounts on Linkedin, Facebook and Twitter, directions to the Chamber office, and much more to help you conduct business. Join us today!  Green Bay Packers, JackRussellApps, smart phone apps, Apple iphone, ipod, ipad3, Android, Tablet, Blackberry, Kindle Fire, Apple TV, Jack Russell Terrier, Aaron Rodgers
